<section class="diff" id="diff">
  <div class="diff-inner">
    <div class="diff-header">
      <h2 class="diff-title">
        Built <em>differently.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="diff-sub">Not another async video tool. Not another transcript app. Something else.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="diff-stack">

      <div class="diff-row">
        <div class="diff-headline">
          <span class="strike">Async video.</span><br/>
          <em>A real conversation.</em>
        </div>
        <div class="diff-body">
          Async video tools record candidates answering preset questions into the void. They don't
          adapt, they don't probe, they don't follow up. <strong>AnyInterview talks back</strong> —
          asks follow-ups when an answer is thin, adapts to what the interviewee actually says.
          It's a conversation, not a recital.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="diff-row">
        <div class="diff-headline">
          <span class="strike">A transcription tool.</span><br/>
          <em>A conversation that runs itself.</em>
        </div>
        <div class="diff-body">
          Otter records meetings you've already taken. Fireflies summarizes calls you already conducted.
          <strong>AnyInterview conducts the call.</strong> The transcript and summary are the byproduct,
          not the product. The bottleneck wasn't documentation — it was finding time to have the
          conversation in the first place.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="diff-row">
        <div class="diff-headline">
          <span class="strike">Just hiring.</span><br/>
          <em>Any structured conversation worth having more of.</em>
        </div>
        <div class="diff-body">
          Most interview tools only do hiring — and only one kind of hiring. <strong>AnyInterview is
          built for the whole shape of the problem</strong>: recruiting, research, discovery, audit,
          intake, exit, and everywhere structured conversations are the bottleneck. The unscalable
          part is the same in all of them. So is the fix.
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section.diff {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: clamp(80px, 12vh, 140px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 56px);
  }

  .diff-inner {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .diff-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: clamp(56px, 8vh, 88px);
  }

  h2.diff-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.6vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  h2.diff-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .diff-sub {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.4vw, 19px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-top: 18px;
  }

  .diff-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .diff-row {
    background: var(--field-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(24px, 4vw, 56px);
    align-items: start;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
    position: relative;
  }
  .diff-row.in-view {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  .diff-row:hover {
    background: var(--white);
    border-color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
  .diff-row::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 28px;
    left: -1px;
    width: 3px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0 2px 2px 0;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .diff-headline {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.8vw, 32px);
    line-height: 1.18;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .diff-headline .strike {
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    text-decoration: line-through;
    text-decoration-color: var(--ink-faint);
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .diff-headline em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .diff-body {
    font-size: 15.5px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .diff-body strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .diff-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  }
</style>
